{"node_id": "03698248", "title": "7. Test the API", "path": "local-server > Run a local server > 7. Test the API", "content": "<Tabs>\n  <Tab title=\"Python SDK (async)\">\n    1. Install the LangGraph Python SDK:\n       ```shell  theme={null}\n       pip install langgraph-sdk\n       ```\n    2. Send a message to the assistant (threadless run):\n       ```python  theme={null}\n       from langgraph_sdk import get_client\n       import asyncio\n\n       client = get_client(url=\"http://localhost:2024\")\n\n       async def main():\n           async for chunk in client.runs.stream(\n               None,  # Threadless run\n               \"agent\", # Name of assistant. Defined in langgraph.json.\n               input={\n               \"messages\": [{\n                   \"role\": \"human\",\n                   \"content\": \"What is LangGraph?\",\n                   }],\n               },\n           ):\n               print(f\"Receiving new event of type: {chunk.event}...\")\n               print(chunk.data)\n               print(\"\\n\\n\")\n\n       asyncio.run(main())\n       ```\n  </Tab>\n\n  <Tab title=\"Python SDK (sync)\">\n    1. Install the LangGraph Python SDK:\n       ```shell  theme={null}\n       pip install langgraph-sdk\n       ```\n    2. Send a message to the assistant (threadless run):\n       ```python  theme={null}\n       from langgraph_sdk import get_sync_client\n\n       client = get_sync_client(url=\"http://localhost:2024\")\n\n       for chunk in client.runs.stream(\n           None,  # Threadless run\n           \"agent\", # Name of assistant. Defined in langgraph.json.\n           input={\n               \"messages\": [{\n                   \"role\": \"human\",\n                   \"content\": \"What is LangGraph?\",\n               }],\n           },\n           stream_mode=\"messages-tuple\",\n       ):\n           print(f\"Receiving new event of type: {chunk.event}...\")\n           print(chunk.data)\n           print(\"\\n\\n\")\n       ```\n  </Tab>\n\n  <Tab title=\"Rest API\">\n    ```bash  theme={null}\n    curl -s --request POST \\\n        --url \"http://localhost:2024/runs/stream\" \\\n        --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n        --data \"{\n            \\\"assistant_id\\\": \\\"agent\\\",\n            \\\"input\\\": {\n                \\\"messages\\\": [\n                    {\n                        \\\"role\\\": \\\"human\\\",\n                        \\\"content\\\": \\\"What is LangGraph?\\\"\n                    }\n                ]\n            },\n            \\\"stream_mode\\\": \\\"messages-tuple\\\"\n        }\"\n    ```\n  </Tab>\n</Tabs>", "summary": "Instructions for testing a local LangGraph API using Python SDK (async/sync) and REST API with example code.", "keywords": ["LangGraph", "Python SDK", "REST API", "threadless run", "assistant", "stream", "client.runs.stream", "langgraph.json", "async", "sync"]}